time complexity: O(n log n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: The solution iterates over numbers from 1 to n, calculates the sum of their digits, and counts the occurrences of each sum. It keeps track of the maximum count and the number of sums that have this maximum count, resulting in a straightforward and efficient solution.
